{"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents29OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminateV","roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Layouts","type":"heading","anchor":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inverse"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indeterminate"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": mike a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need a checkbox with only two states to manage use instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but this component must not be considered as disabled.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Bazinga!\", helper: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection,","                                  label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                                  helper: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                                  isReversed: true,","                                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection,","                                  label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                                  isError: true,","                                  errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label and and icon but with the icon flipped vertically","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"level":2,"text":"Suggestions","type":"heading","anchor":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox\/b\/6578e5\/t\/3dd013a529","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"level":3,"text":"Orange","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Wireframe"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.3.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/init(selection:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Initializers"},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/body"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitemindeterminate"]}],"references":{"component_checkboxItem_Orange":{"type":"image","alt":"A checkbox item component in light and dark mode with Orange theme","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_checkboxItem_Orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Orange"},"https://unified-design-system.orange.com/472794e18/p/23f1c1-checkbox":{"type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox","title":"unified-design-system.orange.com"},"component_c